    "The content of the text can have an important bearing on the success of campaigns.",
    "A crucial challenge, therefore, is ensuring that campaign text communicates the correct messages to ensure funders are convinced to invest in the campaign.",
    "Previous research has identified stylistic characteristics such as the richness and persuasiveness of text (Yeh et al., 2019) and its conciseness (Greenberg et al., 2013) to improve success, while spelling errors or informal language can have the opposite effect (Mollick, 2014).",
    "An important but under-researched topic is content analysis that would reveal how founders can signal quality, preparedness and legitimacy, to ensure funders value the product, accept the risk of investing before production and trust the founder to deliver on their promise.",
